# Introduction

Repository holds simple Rest API embeding server which can be used to get embedings of plain text content.

## What is purposes of this?

With it you can get embedings using Rest API `all-MiniLM-L6-v2` model. After that you can save embedings in Vector database.

## Usage

`docker-compose -f docker-compose.yml up -d`

## To get embedings for single document

CURL Request

```shell
curl -X POST http://localhost:9710/embed_query -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"query":"How can I create an account in live helper chat automated hosting?"}'
```

## To get embedings for multiple documents at once

```shell
curl -X POST http://localhost:9710/embed_documents -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"docs":["How can I create an account in live helper chat automated hosting?","What is paid support fee?"]}'
```
